com.chdryra.android.reviewer

Class ReviewEditable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chdryra.android.reviewer.ReviewEditable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Review
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReviewNull, ReviewTreeEditable, ReviewUserEditable

    public abstract class ReviewEditable
extends java.lang.Object
implements Review
    Base class for reviews that allow editing of the data they hold. Adds setters and deleters to the Review interface. ReviewEditables are by definition not published themselves. Use the publish method to return a published ReviewNode of its current data.
